12614","tid":2059886,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http://vimg.nosdn.127.net/snapshot/20180805/HQMoj111d_cover.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=75&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fvimg.nosdn.127.net%2Fsnapshot%2F20180805%2FHQMoj111d_cover.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D75%26type%3Djpg&h=faac3cf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6f441dc8777611dab931039191b00bb553c372f","tid":2059886,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:59:51.000Z","msg":"辯方質疑警員證供出現多個版本，例如警員昨天供稱曾於湯的背包中找到頭盔及防毒面罩，惟今天卻改口指頭盔及面罩是扣於背包上；警員早前又曾聲稱沒有留意少女攀爬鐵絲網的動作，惟事後卻指少女已經落地；經辯方連番質問下，他再次改口，指少女當時未完全落地。辯方向警員直言：「你啲口供，一路講，一路作。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先唔好講單單出現係現場同著無被禁止既衫證唔證明到佢地有暴動<br />\n<br />\n根本d證據都一時一樣，完全無可信性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e34637b58994c7d3649d72d389708f3f0e26bfe","tid":2059886,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:50:39.000Z","msg":"10:05 郭官裁定表證成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}